## 🏗️ 구현 설계

### Statement 확장

```rust
pub enum Statement {
    Let { name: String, value: Expression },
    Expression(Expression),
    Return(Expression),
    If {                           // ← v14.6 추가
        condition: Expression,
        consequence: Vec<Statement>,
        alternative: Option<Vec<Statement>>,
    },
    While {                        // ← v14.6 추가
        condition: Expression,
        body: Vec<Statement>,
    },
    Break,                         // ← v14.6 추가
}
```

### Evaluator 메서드

#### if-else 평가

```rust
fn eval_if_statement(
    &self,
    condition: &Expression,
    consequence: &[Statement],
    alternative: &Option<Vec<Statement>>,
    env: &mut Environment,
) -> Result<FunctionObject, String> {
    // 1. 조건 평가
    let condition_obj = self.eval_expression_simple(condition, env)?;

    // 2. Truthiness 판정
    if self.is_truthy(&condition_obj) {
        // 3. consequence 실행
        let mut block_env = FunctionEnvironment::extend(env.clone());
        self.eval_statements(consequence, &mut block_env)
    } else if let Some(alt) = alternative {
        // 4. alternative 실행
        let mut block_env = FunctionEnvironment::extend(env.clone());
        self.eval_statements(alt, &mut block_env)
    } else {
        Ok(FunctionObject::Null)
    }
}
```

#### while 루프 평가

```rust
fn eval_while_statement(
    &self,
    condition: &Expression,
    body: &[Statement],
    env: &mut Environment,
) -> Result<FunctionObject, String> {
    let max_iterations = 100000;
    let mut iterations = 0;
    let mut result = FunctionObject::Null;

    loop {
        // 1. 반복 제한 확인
        if iterations >= max_iterations {
            return Err("infinite loop detected".to_string());
        }
        iterations += 1;

        // 2. 조건 평가
        let condition_obj = self.eval_expression_simple(condition, env)?;
        if !self.is_truthy(&condition_obj) {
            break;  // 조건이 false면 루프 종료
        }

        // 3. 본문 실행
        let mut block_env = FunctionEnvironment::extend(env.clone());
        result = self.eval_statements(body, &mut block_env)?;

        // break 처리 필요시 추가
    }

    Ok(result)
}
```

